Chilean hosts:
Accipiter chilensis Philippi & Landbeck, 1864
;
Buteo polyosoma (Quoy & Gaimard, 1824)
;
Buteo ventralis Gould, 1837
;
Columba livia Gmelin, 1789
;
Geranoaetus melanoleucus Vieillot, 1819
.

Other hosts: Over 50 species in the orders Columbiformes , Falconiformes and Strigiformes (see
Price et al . 2003: 102
).

